    div.box
      h2 Use-cases
      p The Alpakka controller could be for you if:
      ul
        li You want to play FPS games on the sofa.
        li You want to play mouse-cursor games (eg RTS or city builders) on the sofa.
        li It is difficult for you to use a keyboard.
        li It is difficult for you to use a thumbstick for aiming.
        li You have special needs that require controller modifications.
        li You are interested in a more natural way to aim (actually aiming at things / similar to VR) than traditional input methods.

